name: <color=#A8D0FF>/spawn</color>
description: Teleport to the server's main spawn point.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/warps</color>
description: View the list of all available warps.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/warp</color>
description: Teleport to a specific warp location.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/homes</color>
description: View your list of saved homes.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/home</color>
description: Teleport to one of your saved homes.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/back</color>

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/balance</color>

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/baltop</color>
description: View the top players by balance.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/dback</color>
description: Return to your death location.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/ignore</color>
description: Ignore messages from a player.

name: <color=#D9B3FF>/kits</color>

name: <color=#D9B3FF>/kit</color>
description: Get a kit if you have permission, or preview it.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/mail send</color>
description: Send a mail message to a player.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/mail read</color>
description: Read your mail messages.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/mail clear</color>
description: Clear all your mail messages.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/mail sendtemp</color>
description: Send a temporary mail message with a time limit.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/msg</color>
description: Send a private message to a player.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/nick</color>
description: Change your nickname or reset it.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/pay</color>
description: Pay another player money.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/playtime</color>
description: Check how long you have played on the server.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/playtimetop</color>
description: View the top players by playtime.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/prewards</color>
description: Claim your playtime rewards.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/removehome</color>
description: Delete one of your saved homes.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/reply</color>
description: Reply to the last private message you received.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/sell</color>
description: Sell items from your inventory.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/sit</color>
description: Sit down in your current location.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/sethome</color>
description: Save your current location as a home.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/tpa</color>
description: Request to teleport to another player.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/tpaccept</color>
description: Accept a teleport request.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/tpahere</color>
description: Request a player to teleport to you.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/tpdeny</color>
description: Deny a teleport request.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/votes</color>
description: Check the number of votes a player has.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/votetop</color>
description: View the top voters on the server.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/worth</color>
description: Check the sell value of items.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/worthlist</color>
description: View the list of sell values for all items.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/ranks</color>
description: Teleport to the hall displaying all available ranks.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/crates</color>
description: Teleport to the location where all crates are found.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/store</color>
description: Open the LÉ„nit Market, the server's virtual store.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/discord</color>
description: Get the link to join the Moon PIXELS discord.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/vote</color>
description: Get the server voting link.

name: <color=#A8D0FF>/rules</color>
description: View the server rules.

name: <color=#7FDBFF>/quests</color>
description: Open the quests menu (daily, weekly, universal quests).

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/pwarps</color>
description: Open the player warps menu.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/pwarps create</color>
description: Create a new player warp.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/pwarps delete</color>
description: Delete an existing player warp.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/pwarps edit</color>
description: Open the warp editor for a player warp.

description: Teleport to a specific player warp.

name: <color=#B6E3B6>/pwarps info</color>
description: Get information about a player warp.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah</color>
description: Open the auction house interface.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah expire</color>
description: View your expired auction items.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah collect</color>
description: Collect items you won or that expired in auctions.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah listed</color>
description: View items you are currently selling in auctions.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah view</color>
description: View items being sold by a specific player.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah bid</color>
description: Place a bid on the item in your hand.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/ah sell</color>
description: Sell the item in your hand via the auction house.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/geyser offhand</color>
description: Switch the current item to offhand (Bedrock/Pocket Edition players).

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/geyser ping</color>
description: Show accurate ping for Bedrock/Pocket Edition players.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/pvp</color>
description: Toggle your PvP status.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/abandonclaim</color>
description: Delete the land claim you are standing in.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/claimexplosions</color>
description: Toggle explosions inside your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/trust</color>
description: Allow a player to build and edit in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/untrust</color>
description: Remove a player's build permissions in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/accesstrust</color>
description: Allow a player to use buttons, levers, and beds in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/containertrust</color>
description: Allow a player to use containers, animals, and interact with mechanisms in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/trustlist</color>
description: View the list of players trusted in your current claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/subdivideclaims</color>
description: Enable subdivision mode for your shovel to create subclaims.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/restrictsubclaim</color>
description: Make a subclaim inherit no permissions from its parent claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/basicclaims</color>
description: Switch your shovel back to basic claim mode.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/permissiontrust</color>
description: Allow a player to share their permission level with others in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/untrust all</color>
description: Remove all permissions from all players in your claim.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/abandonallclaims</color>
description: Delete all your land claims.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/buyclaimblocks</color>
description: Convert server money to claim blocks.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/sellclaimblocks</color>
description: Convert claim blocks back to server money.

name: <color=#FFDD57>/claimslist</color>
description: View a player's claims and claim block details.

name: <color=#C7C9CA>/trapped</color>
description: Get out of a land claim where you are trapped.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/chestshop create</color>
description: Create a new chest shop.

name: <color=#FFE3A3>/chestshop add</color>
description: Allow a player to refill stock in your chest shop.
